ets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/fb2906be2ffa51afba2beb905bb59f32-kix.ox6x0z41gqba-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/fb2906be2ffa51afba2beb905bb59f32-kix.ox6x0z41gqba-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/fb2906be2ffa51afba2beb905bb59f32-kix.ox6x0z41gqba-jpg.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/fb2906be2ffa51afba2beb905bb59f32-kix.ox6x0z41gqba-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/fb2906be2ffa51afba2beb905bb59f32-kix.ox6x0z41gqba-768x432.webp 768w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> （来自<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000747.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">试镜信息</a>）</p><p> <strong>VTA（虚拟人才学院）</strong>也计划加大力度。通过持续不断的海选，吸引广泛的人才，每年选出50至60名候选人。此外，我们还针对具有更多独特才能的VTuber举办选拔赛，例如<strong>超级精英车手选拔赛、吉祥物车手选拔赛、双人选拔赛等</strong>，旨在培养不同于现有VTuber的粉丝群体。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.w3jsam4lzagv-300x169.png"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> VTuber培养项目“Virtual Talent Academy（VTA）”和“NIJISANJI EN”的人才选拔即将举行！</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">运营 VTuber 机构“Nijisanji”的 ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 将举办人才培养项目“Virtual Talent Academy (VTA)”的选拔赛，并将隶属于英语 VTuber 项目“NIJISANJI EN”[…]</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2"><span class="text-muted small ml-1">虹山寺2023.11.17</span></span> </div></div></div><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-