oads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-1024x563.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-1024x563.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-300x165.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-768x422.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-1536x845.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.2rm6jgvpgcis-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="563" /></a></p><p> Hololive与GiGO集团的第二次合作活动“hololive x GiGO Campaign ~Neporabo and Outing~”将于6月22日（周六）至7月28日（周日）举行。</p><p>凡在符合条件的抓娃娃机游戏上消费满 500 日元，即可获得原创新奇作品。</p><p>除了活动开始外，GiGO独家娃娃机奖品也将陆续推出，合作鲷鱼烧“Hololive Yaki ~Nepo Lab~第2版”也将发售。</p><p> ©️ 2016 COVER 公司<br />© GENDA GiGO Entertainment Inc. 保留所有权利。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000699.000034930.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GENDA GiGO Entertainment Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2>宗谷一花将连续六个月发行歌曲</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.y1fh526cbkfm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.y1fh526cbkfm-1024x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.y1fh526cbkfm-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c4636572dfa7c654c152b0ac0858-kix.y1fh526cbkfm-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/5082c46